        <h1 style={{ fontSize: "clamp(56px, 12vw, 110px)", fontWeight: 800, lineHeight: 0.95, margin: "0 0 32px", color: RED, letterSpacing: "-0.03em", textShadow: "0 0 60px rgba(232,0,13,0.35)" }}>GASTRONOMİ</h1>

